{"type": "article", "id": 21804, "title": "春节快到了，国外时尚品牌的红包都长什么样？", "description": "在这个直接手机发红包的年代，想讨好消费者，还是得用点心呐！", "date": "2016-02-03T15:06:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 6467, "name": "红包"}, {"id": 9012, "name": "时尚品牌"}, {"id": 23085, "name": "欧美"}, {"id": 6945, "name": "春节"}, {"id": 143, "name": "设计"}, {"id": 189, "name": "Burberry"}, {"id": 23086, "name": "Kath"}], "category": 19, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 146, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607145847QX1xq2hTjtuRk5gi.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">快过年啦，最近大家可能被猴年有关的新闻刷屏了，各大品牌都推出了带有猴子形象的产品，从化妆品包装到包袋、手机壳、运动鞋……这些洋品牌对于中国传统元素的演绎是千差万别。（<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/20540.html\">但，好像让人受到惊吓的比较多</a>。）</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607145838CcWi4TkydtHXhjgv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.83958333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">这种时候他们还会纷纷推出红包，送给消费者以表心意，有的奢侈品牌推出的红包只送给 VIP 顾客或者消费达到一定金额的， 不过，这可都是他们变着法子讨好中国消费者的。虽然也没谁会为了赠送的纸质红包多消费，但也算是一处细节。</p>\n<p class=\"\">一起来看看今年这些品牌们都如何设计红包。</p>\n<h2>1.Burberry</h2>\n<p class=\"\"> Burberry 的包装目前看来应该是最精美的，而且没有硬要和“猴”产生关联。每封金色的红包上还有品牌最经典的格纹，花朵一般的渐变粉红色纸壳象征“花开富贵”。最外层的封套加上了个粉色的蝴蝶结缎带，这样的红包还是挺讲究的。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607145839XgIOZPwVcSbsWYM2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607145840yosr974uit2hQPF0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.53583618\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<h2>2. Tiffany</h2>\n<p class=\"\">再来一个不是大红的，Tiffany 维持了自己最标志性的 Tiffany Blue。表面还烫金上了类似海洋波浪的图腾。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607145841nEHmK40S7R5fGBUT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.564\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<h2>3.Kate Spade</h2>\n<p class=\"\">Kate Spade 用了品牌常见的粉色与红色竖条纹相间，乍一看像是维多利亚秘密旗下的 Pink 出过的一款手机壳。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607145841twK7aiOZRC6MY9Vu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<h2>Fendi </h2>\n<p class=\"\">金色银色兼有的红包外面，点缀富有童趣的拼贴花朵，也是品牌近来很爱的元素。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607145842DAQ7yXIh1tzObegM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57436399\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n<h2>Alice + Olivia </h2>\n<p class=\"\">创始人 Stacey Bendet 的卡通自画像可谓是品牌最据标志性的元素，大墨镜和红唇也被印在了红包上，打开红包还会出现她的包头。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607145842RHGe8bW3qfsOuP6m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63986014\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<h2>Cath Kidston </h2>\n<p>这个以小碎花包包出名的品牌，红包也不忘用粉花点缀。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607145843UvtKiyHDz5GmA9T6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n<h2>Louis Vuitton </h2>\n<p>红包正面很普通，烫金的品牌名称，背面做成包包搭扣的样式蛮特别。不过他们好像用这样的设计很多次了。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607145843YVPQldhcUE1AiI8b.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.43496802\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">最后，今年有很多品牌都用到了猴子的元素，且红得耀眼，放在一起说。像是 Paul Smith 啊：</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607145844x62ZimAKXbSNtJWc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">爱马仕抽象的猴子形象不难看：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607145845t5Mcpvbf1hTQuOjD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62446352\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">Giorgio Armani 也太随意了，方形的红包，背面印着一个“猴”字和年份就结束了。La Mer 红色和金色两款，正中间一幅带有猴子的剪纸图案。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607145846wSCUvNMXfETn2Qyg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.58541893\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n<p class=\"\">题图来源：<a jsaction=\"mousedown:irc.rl;keydown:irc.rlk\" data-noload=\"\" href=\"http://yannkam.blogspot.com/2015/02/creative-chinese-zodiac-sheep-year-red.html\" data-ved=\"0ahUKEwjguZyGgtvKAhVGJKYKHdFkBJAQjB0ICDAA\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">yannkam.blogspot</a></p>\n\n\n"}